Other libraries
---------------

For alternatives, check out [this detailed list of PDF-related Python libs by Patrick Maupin](https://github.com/pmaupin/pdfrw#other-libraries). There is also `pikepdf`, `PyFPDF2` & `WeasyPrint`.


